    "created_at": "2015-02-11T06:06:33Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-02-11T14:10:24Z",
    "body": "Bummer, I'm getting little white caps at the top even when `show:true` is set. Calling `setSize` didn't do the trick either.\n\n![white corners](https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/9297096/white-corners.png)\n\nIs anyone else seeing this behavior currently?\n\n---\n\nEDIT: I was able to get rid of the shiny white corners by setting `transparent: true` on the window options.\n"
