    "created_at": "2015-03-23T23:07:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-03-23T23:07:13Z",
    "body": "This definitely doesn't happen if you construct the window with show: true. It also doesn't occur if you resize the window, after a certain point the squared corners disappear.\n\nI think it's important that this rounding remain, as it's the default way that all windows are displayed in OSX and little details like square corners standout as making the app 'feel' not native.\n"
